    },
    {
        "Sixth": "sixth crusade"
    },
    {
        " Crusades in the Holy Land.         By mid42 around 42 Crusaders had gathered in ": null
    },
    {
        "Lyon": "lyon"
    },
    {
        " before marching south. Many Crusaders stayed on for no more than 42 days before being replaced. A large number came from Northern France, while some had volunteered from England. The crusaders turned towards ": null
